column5:
See (v1) for the original Angel's version and the article's history
  background. Changes: different priors for zero frequency; Fig. 5 redrawn;
  Section VI renamed and extended; App. B extended by non-factorizable priors;
  Added Apps. D, E, F, G, and H, and 9 references; Style and format changes
  throughout. Many of these changes reflect a year of experience in applying
  the theory to real-world data
